{"tid":2092893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加山傳播份聲明算唔算跪底...","createTime":"2020-07-03T13:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T13:33:58.000Z","uid":246044,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"78e91d56b637a0cde82e88715253c56cae0a9d0b","tid":2092893,"uid":246044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:06:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/dbchannel.hk/photos/a.122771689139239/274063860676687\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdbchannel.hk%2Fphotos%2Fa.122771689139239%2F274063860676687&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXK0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=4baf2655\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/dbchannel.hk/photos/a.122771689139239/274063860676687</a><br />\n<br />\n【《加山傳播》就報導引起關注及震怒之聲明】<br />\n<br />\n就前日(1)下午警方，不點名向譴責本台一篇新聞的用字，本台對此有幾點回應。<br />\n<br />\n1. 本台一直堅信香港為法治社會，故在香港行普通法的原則下，我們對任何事項均採取無罪推定的原則，是故只能採用「附近市民」的字眼。<br />\n<br />\n2. 就「同行友人」一詞，據本台記者親耳所聞，事發時曾聽到有人喊出「啊sir我同佢嚟行街咋」，而當時所有人都在行人路上，依照無罪推定的原則，本台編輯部亦只能以此最中性的字眼作描述。<br />\n<br />\n3. 最後就標題中「市民合力擊退落單警」，依上述解釋，「市民合力」乃描述事實。即使該些市民懷疑犯法，甚至被定性為「暴徒」，他們依然是香港市民，兩者並無相沖。<br />\n<br />\n而「落單警」一詞，記者印象中其他警員距離受襲警員，最多只有20米距離，若看見同袍遇襲，理應能馬上上前支援，故編輯部認為「落單警」為客觀描述。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">傳媒具有社會責任報道真相，昨日報導未盡全面，選字方面或引誤會，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《加山傳播》對此感到難過及遺憾</span>。《加山傳播》必會接受各界的善意指導，會繼續緊守崗位，傳承理念。</span><br />\n<br />\n《加山傳播》編輯部<br />\n2020年7月3日<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：Greenday -- Boulevard of Broken Dreams<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xvg7kRc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvg7kRc.png&h=503c2003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個搞得幾好嘅網媒都頂唔住壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0ed96c8e010d7922cba7f808be0d23dbd01bde","tid":2092893,"uid":6253,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:08:38.000Z","msg":"門面說話姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3382c5cc14bad51169547f113bb54739c98c9ae0","tid":2092893,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:11:02.000Z","msg":"咁都叫跪，樓主要求幾高"},{"pid":"5838dee3775f89154b0a846130e5db079d90bc0b","tid":2092893,"uid":4965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:13:56.000Z","msg":"黃絲叫佢地刪相就口響 到人地比狗屌無人幫口<br />\n邊個都心灰跪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f3a0d7546457801698ef114e2c318312044c02","tid":2092893,"uid":47309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:15:20.000Z","msg":"咁都叫跪咩"},{"pid":"908cfdc4d27522a15cf10576f15df8b08dc962b6","tid":2092893,"uid":21917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:15:29.000Z","msg":"咪用平時狗方個套姐 有咩問題"},{"pid":"f43d5bb56bcc8e2b1489e6b92e3437ea2bde853e","tid":2092893,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:21:34.000Z","msg":"noted 呢篇嘢就係咁嘅意思"},{"pid":"6835cfe39139532123b31a3ee207e9f60c6d28a1","tid":2092893,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:27:34.000Z","msg":"請問下次再看到記者影手足打狗時，我們要否擋鏡頭？"},{"pid":"8028ff73e2faf65aebf0a3e53461bb140b0a2b20","tid":2092893,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:28:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"26a9f27f3e311a625b5b75d5bff209f9573f5c49","tid":2092893,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:29:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"281615b1eb4ff27895b14f0cd985a6f805c3398a","tid":2092893,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:29:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8322ba0807395dab17f9b13901656e37d4a0098b","tid":2092893,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:29:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fa6b1a1166daec61031f459dba126b7016176ce2","tid":2092893,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03